{"id":2926,"date":"2019-09-14T04:45:18","date_gmt":"2019-09-14T04:45:18","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/?p=2926"},"modified":"2019-12-31T11:00:03","modified_gmt":"2019-12-31T04:00:03","slug":"vai-tro-to-roi-quang-cao","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/vai-tro-to-roi-quang-cao.html\/","title":{"rendered":"Vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o trong Marketing"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_36 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">N\u1ed9i Dung<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: none;\"><label for=\"item\" aria-label=\"Table of Content\"><span style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;width: 35px;height: 30px;justify-content: center;\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"item\"><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/vai-tro-to-roi-quang-cao.html\/#Muc_tieu_chien_dich_marketing\" title=\"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch marketing?\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch marketing?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/vai-tro-to-roi-quang-cao.html\/#Vai_tro_cua_to_roi_quang_cao_trong_Marketing\" title=\"Vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o trong Marketing\">Vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o trong Marketing<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/vai-tro-to-roi-quang-cao.html\/#To_roi_quang_cao_de_dang_truyen_dat_thong_diep_chinh\" title=\"T\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh\">T\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/vai-tro-to-roi-quang-cao.html\/#Huong_nguoi_dung_co_nhung_hanh_dong_tiep_theo_ma_ban_mong_muon\" title=\"H\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ti\u1ebfp theo m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mong mu\u1ed1n\">H\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ti\u1ebfp theo m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mong mu\u1ed1n<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><em>T\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o trong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7n nay th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e0 l\u1ed7i th\u1eddi. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m! <strong>Vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o trong marketing<\/strong> v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea5y cho c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n.<\/em><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Muc_tieu_chien_dich_marketing\"><\/span><strong>M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch marketing?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>C\u00e2u h\u1ecfi t\u1ed5ng quan nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0: B\u1ea1n \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec trong c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c kinh doanh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ngay l\u00fac n\u00e0y? B\u1ea1n mong \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 g\u00ec t\u1eeb ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng marketing? B\u1ea1n \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng hay t\u0103ng nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u? Qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 cho s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u1edbi? T\u0103ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c? Thu th\u1eadp contact kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng?&#8230;<\/p>\n<p>Do \u0111\u00f3, t\u00ednh m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh li\u1ec7u t\u1edd r\u01a1i c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch hay kh\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2927\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2927\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2927\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/vi\u1ec7c-\u0111\u1ea7u-ti\u00ean-lu\u00f4n-c\u1ea7n-l\u00e0m-l\u00e0-x\u00e1c-\u0111\u1ecbnh-m\u1ee5c-ti\u00eau.png\" alt=\"vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o trong marketing\" width=\"825\" height=\"399\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/vi\u1ec7c-\u0111\u1ea7u-ti\u00ean-lu\u00f4n-c\u1ea7n-l\u00e0m-l\u00e0-x\u00e1c-\u0111\u1ecbnh-m\u1ee5c-ti\u00eau.png 620w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/vi\u1ec7c-\u0111\u1ea7u-ti\u00ean-lu\u00f4n-c\u1ea7n-l\u00e0m-l\u00e0-x\u00e1c-\u0111\u1ecbnh-m\u1ee5c-ti\u00eau-300x145.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2927\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean lu\u00f4n c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m l\u00e0 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Vai_tro_cua_to_roi_quang_cao_trong_Marketing\"><\/span><strong>Vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o trong Marketing<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch marketing, ti\u1ebfp theo ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i. T\u1edd r\u01a1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 marketing c\u00f3 chi ph\u00ed th\u1ea5p, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p ho\u1eb7c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1eady t\u1edd r\u01a1i s\u1ebd h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 g\u00ec cho to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch marketing, li\u1ec7u n\u00f3 c\u00f3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1ed5 tr\u1ee3 kh\u00e1c \u0111ang ch\u1ea1y song song kh\u00f4ng? L\u1ee3i \u00edch ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1edd r\u01a1i thay v\u00ec c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2928\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2928\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2928\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/vai-tr\u00f2-c\u1ee7a-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i-qu\u1ea3ng-c\u00e1o-\u0111ang-kh\u00f4ng-\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c-\u0111\u00e1nh-gi\u00e1-\u0111\u00fang.jpg\" alt=\"vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o trong marketing\" width=\"825\" height=\"825\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/vai-tr\u00f2-c\u1ee7a-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i-qu\u1ea3ng-c\u00e1o-\u0111ang-kh\u00f4ng-\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c-\u0111\u00e1nh-gi\u00e1-\u0111\u00fang.jpg 800w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/vai-tr\u00f2-c\u1ee7a-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i-qu\u1ea3ng-c\u00e1o-\u0111ang-kh\u00f4ng-\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c-\u0111\u00e1nh-gi\u00e1-\u0111\u00fang-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/vai-tr\u00f2-c\u1ee7a-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i-qu\u1ea3ng-c\u00e1o-\u0111ang-kh\u00f4ng-\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c-\u0111\u00e1nh-gi\u00e1-\u0111\u00fang-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/vai-tr\u00f2-c\u1ee7a-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i-qu\u1ea3ng-c\u00e1o-\u0111ang-kh\u00f4ng-\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c-\u0111\u00e1nh-gi\u00e1-\u0111\u00fang-768x768.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2928\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00fang<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"To_roi_quang_cao_de_dang_truyen_dat_thong_diep_chinh\"><\/span><strong>T\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi t\u1edbi th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p g\u00ec cho t\u1eadp kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau b\u1ea1n v\u1eeba x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh? B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n g\u1ee3i l\u00ean cho h\u1ecd suy ngh\u0129, c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u00e0 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng g\u00ec? H\u1ecd n\u00ean kh\u1eafc ghi \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n?<\/p>\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c in tr\u00ean thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p duy nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin kh\u00e1c g\u00e2y xao nh\u00e3ng cho th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2921\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/d\u1ecbch-v\u1ee5-thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i-tr\u1ecdn-g\u00f3i-t\u1ea1i-\u00c1-Ch\u00e2u-Media.jpg\" alt=\"vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o trong marketing\" width=\"825\" height=\"825\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/d\u1ecbch-v\u1ee5-thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i-tr\u1ecdn-g\u00f3i-t\u1ea1i-\u00c1-Ch\u00e2u-Media.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/d\u1ecbch-v\u1ee5-thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i-tr\u1ecdn-g\u00f3i-t\u1ea1i-\u00c1-Ch\u00e2u-Media-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/d\u1ecbch-v\u1ee5-thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i-tr\u1ecdn-g\u00f3i-t\u1ea1i-\u00c1-Ch\u00e2u-Media-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/d\u1ecbch-v\u1ee5-thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i-tr\u1ecdn-g\u00f3i-t\u1ea1i-\u00c1-Ch\u00e2u-Media-768x768.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Huong_nguoi_dung_co_nhung_hanh_dong_tiep_theo_ma_ban_mong_muon\"><\/span><strong>H\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ti\u1ebfp theo m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mong mu\u1ed1n<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 m\u00ecnh mong mu\u1ed1n kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng g\u00ec sau khi xem t\u1edd r\u01a1i. V\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n \u0111\u0103ng k\u00ed online \u0111\u1ec3 tham gia hay \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u1ebfn m\u00e3i?<\/p>\n<p>K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 t\u0103ng nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n g\u1ee3i \u00fd cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ti\u1ebfp theo m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 truy c\u1eadp v\u00e0o trang web \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam ho\u1eb7c theo d\u00f5i b\u1ea1n tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt tin t\u1ee9c \u2013 h\u00e3y l\u00e0m cho m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 th\u1eadt d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng l\u00e0m theo.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2930\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2930\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2930\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/s\u1ef1-\u0111i\u1ec1u-h\u01b0\u1edbng-\u0111\u1ed1i-v\u1edbi-kh\u00e1ch-h\u00e0ng-d\u1ec5-theo-d\u00f5i.jpg\" alt=\"s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng d\u1ec5 theo d\u00f5i\" width=\"825\" height=\"612\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/s\u1ef1-\u0111i\u1ec1u-h\u01b0\u1edbng-\u0111\u1ed1i-v\u1edbi-kh\u00e1ch-h\u00e0ng-d\u1ec5-theo-d\u00f5i.jpg 600w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/s\u1ef1-\u0111i\u1ec1u-h\u01b0\u1edbng-\u0111\u1ed1i-v\u1edbi-kh\u00e1ch-h\u00e0ng-d\u1ec5-theo-d\u00f5i-300x223.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2930\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng d\u1ec5 theo d\u00f5i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><em>Xem th\u00eam <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-thiet-ke-to-roi.html\/\">D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i tr\u1ecdn g\u00f3i c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n<p><em>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i <strong>vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o trong Marketing<\/strong> l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng online hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 chi ph\u00ed \u00edt t\u1ed1n k\u00e9m h\u01a1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean t\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p. \u0110\u1ea7u t\u01b0 cho t\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 l\u1ed7i th\u1eddi.\u00a0<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>T\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o trong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7n nay th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e0 l\u1ed7i th\u1eddi. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m! Vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o trong marketing v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea5y cho c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n. M\u1ee5c&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2931,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[51,56],"tags":[228,105,229,227],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v18.7 (Yoast SEO v19.9) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o trong Marketing - \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media Digital Marketing<\/t